      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total showstopper! This beauty is in truly mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, keeping it garage-stored and hand-washed only. It looks, smells, and drives like it\u2019s brand new, with zero scratches or dings to speak of. If you\u2019ve been looking for that 'perfect' find, this is definitely the one! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your dream car!",
      "price": 43500.0,
